{"ECRASEMENT":[{"def":"The operation performed with an écraseur.","pos":""}],"ECRASEUR":[{"def":"An instrument intended to replace the knife in many operations, the parts operated on being severed by the crushing effect produced by the gradual tightening of a steel chain, so that hemorrhage rarely follows.","pos":""}],"ECRU":[{"def":"Having the color or appearance of unbleached stuff, as silk, linen, or the like.","pos":""}]}